    "title": "UN nuclear boss says inspectors will visit Iran sites, as Tehran says only after a final deal",
    "description": "TOKYO: The head of the UN’s nuclear agency signaled Wednesday that Iranian nuclear enrichment sites would be visited by his inspectors, a key component in the interim US-Iran to reach an end to the war. But an Iranian diplomat promptly rejected this, saying such a visit can only come after a final deal — a denial that highlighted the precariousness of the ongoing negotiations.",
